folder: Woodhave Blvd & Furmanville Avenue, Queens, NY
text:
Woodhaven Boulevard, west side, north of Furmanville Avenue, showing on the west side of the Boulevard in order are the homes of Edward Tompkins 1852, H. Hasselberger 1873, J.J. Tompkins 1891, and J.T. Tompkins 1896-1909; Adam Geier 1873-1891, and William and Katherine Geyer in 1909; Michael Steinler 1873 to 1909; on the east side is the J.S. Hiller house of 1891. Francis Meyer was the owner in 1909.

April 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
